>> source: https://www.southernliving.com/beau-monde-seasoning-11705735
>> serves: 1
>> image: https://www.southernliving.com/thmb/qsQPZ0Pj-9JvuRgGc8FjRtILaGw=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/Beau-monde-seasoning_SEO4_beauty_01-1a01a822698f4684b32de6ed8e317ab0.jpg

Place @celery seeds{2%Tbsp}, @granulated onion{2%Tbsp}, @kosher salt{2%Tbsp}, and @granulated sugar{1%tsp} in a #spice grinder{} and process until finely ground and powdery (about ~{30%seconds}).

Alternatively, you can also use a #mortar and pestle{} to pound and grind the ingredients into a fine powder.

Store the seasoning in an #airtight container{} at room temperature for up to 6 months.
